Voice chatbot pipeline with transcription + LLM + TTS:

```json
{
  "summary": "Voice chatbot with STT and TTS",
  "pipeline": [
    {"step": 1, "image": "hive/http-input:latest", "role": "ingress", "notes": "Receive audio input"},
    {"step": 2, "role": "transcribe", "notes": "Audio node: action=transcribe, provider=openai, model=whisper-1"},
    {"step": 3, "image": "hive/memory-agent:latest", "role": "recall", "notes": "Load conversation history"},
    {"step": 4, "image": "hive/llm-agent:latest", "role": "respond", "notes": "Generate text response"},
    {"step": 5, "image": "hive/memory-agent:latest", "role": "store", "notes": "Save new exchange"},
    {"step": 6, "role": "tts", "notes": "Audio node: action=tts, provider=openai, model=tts-1, voice=nova"},
    {"step": 7, "image": "hive/http-output:latest", "role": "egress", "notes": "Return audio response"}
  ],
  "agent_config_hints": {
    "llm": {"temperature": 0.7, "systemPrompt": "You are a friendly voice assistant. Keep responses concise and conversational."},
    "memory": {"type": "buffer", "bufferSize": 10}
  },
  "needs_human_review": false
}
```

The Audio node appears twice: once for transcription (STT) and once for speech synthesis (TTS). The LLM processes text in between.

Pipeline de transcription et resume de reunion :

```json
{
  "summary": "Transcription de reunion avec resume et actions",
  "pipeline": [
    {"step": 1, "image": "hive/http-input:latest", "role": "ingress", "notes": "Upload audio de la reunion"},
    {"step": 2, "role": "transcribe", "notes": "Audio node: action=transcribe, model=whisper-1"},
    {"step": 3, "image": "hive/llm-agent:latest", "role": "summarize", "notes": "Generer resume structure"},
    {"step": 4, "image": "hive/output-parser:latest", "role": "parse", "notes": "Extraire JSON: {resume, actions[], participants[]}"},
    {"step": 5, "image": "hive/db-connector:latest", "role": "store", "notes": "Sauvegarder en base"},
    {"step": 6, "image": "hive/http-output:latest", "role": "egress"}
  ],
  "agent_config_hints": {
    "llm": {
      "temperature": 0,
      "systemPrompt": "Tu es un assistant de reunion. A partir de la transcription, genere: 1) un resume en 3-5 points, 2) une liste d'actions avec responsable et deadline, 3) la liste des participants mentionnes. Reponds en JSON."
    }
  },
  "needs_human_review": false
}
```

Le noeud Audio transcrit l'enregistrement, le LLM analyse et structure, l'output-parser valide le JSON, et le db-connector sauvegarde.
